@dpsBase = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@authToken = user_token_123

### Fragmentos por pregunta — solo semántico (POST /api/v1/fragment-query/by-question)
POST {{dpsBase}}/fragment-query/by-question
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "chat_id": 1,
  "semantic_queries": [
    {
      "text": "Avión de caza",
      "max_fragments": 3
    }
  ],
  "bm25_queries": [],
  "rerank": {
    "enabled": false
  }
}


### Híbrido semántico + BM25
POST {{dpsBase}}/fragment-query/by-question
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "semantic_queries": [
    {
      "text": "caza multirrol",
      "max_fragments": 5
    }
  ],
  "bm25_queries": [
    {
      "text": "Fuerza Aérea",
      "max_fragments": 5
    }
  ],
  "rerank": {
    "enabled": false
  }
}


### Con rerank (max_fragments del rerank no puede superar la suma de max_fragments de las consultas)
POST {{dpsBase}}/fragment-query/by-question
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "chat_id": 1,
  "semantic_queries": [
    {
      "text": "seguridad de la aviación",
      "max_fragments": 8
    }
  ],
  "bm25_queries": [
    {
      "text": "PNSAC",
      "max_fragments": 4
    }
  ],
  "rerank": {
    "enabled": true,
    "max_fragments": 6
  }
}


### Fragmentos por documentos (POST /api/v1/fragment-query/by-documents)
POST {{dpsBase}}/fragment-query/by-documents
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "document_ids": [32]
}
